{"tid":1453592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨用恐怖治國治港， 屈服於恐怖之下我地就輸左。","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:56:04.000Z","uid":43785,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf7ba8ea4a97c2a9488070486e7a141ec37c7f8","tid":1453592,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"共產黨用恐怖治國治港， 屈服於恐怖之下我地就輸左。<br />\n經過721，喺佢哋眼中佢哋覺得香港人係唔驚呢啲恐怖。 佢哋根本好撚頭痕， 越接近10月1號佢哋只會越嚟越變本加厲， 因為10月1號係70週年國慶， 冇人會希望國慶當日會變咗國難日。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，恐怖呢一招十分成功的，當年成吉思汗，ISIS打到成個歐亞洲甚至係世界聞風喪膽， 就係用恐怖去做出黎。<br />\n<br />\n警察一日都唔願意兵變，相信共產黨都一路唔會出解放軍。 依家我哋要做嘅嘢就係要令警察兵變， 就等於贏咗成場抗爭！<br />\n但要共產黨出解放軍， 攪爛自己棵搖錢樹，佢真係寧願批準我哋五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n我明白有啲嘢齋講係冇用，做啦！<br />\n依家就算你用核彈我都支持你！！"},{"pid":"0caa5b2d41fc548ffe337fba2a464b3028345e04","tid":1453592,"uid":153151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkNSJpA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkNSJpA.png&h=b9ad86b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a641fe5cf8eb53d35fc7d75e04aa8016ebaba9a","tid":1453592,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇今日開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355e776fba942a2ca2cd19a6954f03e9d456e825","tid":1453592,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"各位香港人，加油"},{"pid":"3dc9d2eebf856b37d07c1bc3b059f80efbec01c5","tid":1453592,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir帶頭兵變？"},{"pid":"5363628cc1dd5d2b444a008f2c065793c7eb5ad8","tid":1453592,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc9d2eebf856b37d07c1bc3b059f80efbec01c5","tid":1453592,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir帶頭兵變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:55:18.000Z